{
  "texts": [
    "To assess the performance of our proposed architecture, we utilized commonly used metrics for object detection tasks, namely precision, recall, and IoU (Intersection over Union).",
    "These metrics are defined as follows:",
    "P recision = T P/ (T P + F P) (10) backpropagated into the SR network in order to enhance the network learning during training.",
    "The LR-HR images pairs were utilized to train the proposed framework, and the obtained SR images were used to train Faster RCNN detector.",
    "In testing, only LR images were feed to the generator to create SR image to be feed to detector network."
  ]
}